            <b>How much of it is spin, dressed as fact</b> - with so many claims being thrown about it seems impossible to know who to believe
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          So we created Referendum.wtf, which takes elements of both Whip and Explaain: breaking down info into an <a href="#6">easy to understand synopsis</a> and <a href="#9">encouraging participation in politics</a>.
